Crédit Agricole S.A. is a member of 
Crédit Agricole group, one of the largest French 
banking groups and is one of the leading cooperative companies in the world. 
Traditionally focused on providing retail banking products and services in France, 
Crédit Agricole has expanded its positions into corporate and investment banking.




