Credit Agricole S.A. Key Developments

Credit Agricole Is Reported To Sell Part Of Banque Saudi Fransi
Jun 13 17
Credit Agricole S.A. (ENXTPA:ACA) reportedly begun discussions of sale of its 31% stake in Banque Saudi Fransi (SASE:1050), reversing earlier plans to completely exit the business, according to people familiar with the matter. JPMorgan Chase & Co. is advising Credit Agricole on the sale, one of the people said. Credit Agricole and JPMorgan declined to comment.


Crédit Agricole Presents at V-Fi Europe, Jun-21-2017 10:40 AM
Jun 6 17
Crédit Agricole Presents at V-Fi Europe, Jun-21-2017 10:40 AM. Venue: Andaz Hotel, Liverpool Street, London, United Kingdom. Speakers: Emmanuel Danzin, Executive Director, Scarce Resources Advisory.


Crédit Agricole Presents at Goldman Sachs Twenty-First Annual European Financials Conference, Jun-09-2017 09:45 AM
Jun 6 17
Crédit Agricole Presents at Goldman Sachs Twenty-First Annual European Financials Conference, Jun-09-2017 09:45 AM. Venue: The InterContinental Madrid, Paseo De La Castellana 49, Madrid, 28046, Spain. Speakers: Cyril Meilland, Head of IR, Jérôme Grivet, Deputy General Manager & Group CFO.


